WEBVTT

00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:08.000
In a meadow bathed in morning light...

00:00:09.000 --> 00:00:15.000
Big Buck Bunny woke up to greet the day.

00:00:16.000 --> 00:00:23.000
The forest was peaceful, full of butterflies
and blooming flowers.

00:00:26.000 --> 00:00:33.000
He breathed in the fresh air and smiled.

00:00:36.000 --> 00:00:46.000
Nothing could ruin such a perfect morning...

00:00:48.000 --> 00:00:55.000
Or so he thought.

00:00:57.000 --> 00:01:07.000
Three little troublemakers lurked in the shadows.

00:01:10.000 --> 00:01:20.000
Frank the squirrel spotted something tempting.

00:01:22.000 --> 00:01:33.000
He and his gang had a reputation for cruelty.

00:01:36.000 --> 00:01:47.000
Buck noticed the strangers but paid them no mind.

00:01:50.000 --> 00:02:02.000
The rodents exchanged mischievous glances.

00:02:06.000 --> 00:02:18.000
Something wicked was brewing in the forest.

00:02:22.000 --> 00:02:36.000
Buck wandered happily, unaware of what was coming.

00:02:38.000 --> 00:02:44.000
A butterfly caught his eye.

00:02:45.000 --> 00:02:57.000
Frank crushed the butterfly without mercy.

00:02:58.000 --> 00:03:10.000
Buck's joy shattered in an instant.

00:03:12.000 --> 00:03:24.000
The bully laughed and danced around him.

00:03:27.000 --> 00:03:40.000
They pelted him with nuts and ran away giggling.

00:03:46.000 --> 00:04:00.000
Buck stood there, dazed and humiliated.

00:04:03.000 --> 00:04:16.000
A tear rolled down his furry cheek.

00:04:18.000 --> 00:04:27.000
Then something changed in his eyes.

00:04:29.000 --> 00:04:43.000
Buck wiped his tears and made a decision.

00:04:45.000 --> 00:04:58.000
He gathered sticks, vines, and logs from the forest.

00:05:02.000 --> 00:05:17.000
His paws moved with unexpected precision.

00:05:22.000 --> 00:05:37.000
The traps were elaborate. Almost artistic.

00:05:42.000 --> 00:05:56.000
The rodents continued their rampage, unaware.

00:06:00.000 --> 00:06:16.000
Frank kicked another creature for fun.

00:06:18.000 --> 00:06:29.000
They had no idea what was waiting for them.

00:06:31.000 --> 00:06:46.000
Buck lured the first bully with a shiny apple.

00:06:50.000 --> 00:07:03.000
The trap snapped shut. Direct hit.

00:07:06.000 --> 00:07:19.000
The squirrel flew through the air with a shriek.

00:07:23.000 --> 00:07:37.000
The second one followed — caught in a vine snare.

00:07:41.000 --> 00:07:54.000
Rinky the chinchilla got a face full of mud.

00:07:55.000 --> 00:08:11.000
Buck watched calmly. Justice, served.

00:08:13.000 --> 00:08:29.000
The last bully, Frank, tried to flee.

00:08:31.000 --> 00:08:46.000
But Buck had planned ahead.

00:08:51.000 --> 00:09:06.000
A perfectly timed log sent Frank sailing.

00:09:11.000 --> 00:09:26.000
The forest echoed with the sound of karma.

00:09:31.000 --> 00:09:49.000
Buck returned to his meadow.

00:09:51.000 --> 00:10:06.000
The butterflies danced again. The flowers bloomed.

00:10:09.000 --> 00:10:21.000
Peace had been restored to the forest.

00:10:23.000 --> 00:10:33.000
And Big Buck Bunny smiled.
